    ⚡ HOW THE PROGRAM WORKS:
    ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

    🔹 CORE TECHNOLOGY

    Synapse Script Hub works by providing a script execution interface that connects to the Roblox client.  
    After launching the tool, the program attaches to the running Roblox process and loads the script hub environment.

    The built-in script manager allows users to select scripts from a library, load them into memory, and execute them using the integrated Lua interpreter.

    The system is optimized for fast script injection and stable execution while maintaining compatibility with many Roblox experiences.


